) i) Implement DML commands for the following schema
Students (StudentID, StudentName, Major)
ii) creating and querying views

1)Schema Definition
CREATE TABLE Students (
  StudentID INT PRIMARY KEY,
  StudentName VARCHAR(50),
  Major VARCHAR(50)
);

 i) DML Commands (Data Manipulation Language)
